{"word":"ἐξεγγυάω","slug":"ἐξεγγυάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n37040\" key=\"e)ceggua/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐξεγγῠ-άω</orth>, <sense id=\"n37040.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">give up</tr_> a slave <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">on security</tr_> to be examined, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0028.tlg005.perseus-grc1:47\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Antipho\">Antipho</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.47</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">free</tr_> one <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by giving bail for</tr_> him, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg024.perseus-grc1:73\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.73</biblScope> </bibl>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be bailed,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐξεγγυηθέντες κριθῆναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0027.tlg001.perseus-grc1:44\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ And.\">And.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.44</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg019.perseus-grc1:169\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.169</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐφ᾽ οἷς ἐξηγγυήθη</foreign> [to fulfil the conditions] on which <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">security was given,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tl